{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-remark-auto-headers","description":"Gatsby plugin to autolink headers in markdown processed by Remark","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin","remark"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"zido","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/a662a7e575fcac392c4c72f7cd730d96"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/zidoshare/gatsby-remark-auto-headers"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-remark-autolink-headers\"><a href=\"#gatsby-remark-autolink-headers\" aria-label=\"gatsby remark autolink headers permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-remark-autolink-headers</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>it’s forked from <a href=\"https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/edit/master/packages/gatsby-remark-autolink-headers\">gatsby-remark-autolink-headers</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Adds GitHub-style hover links to headers in your markdown files when they’re rendered.</p>\n<p>This is a sub-plugin for <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-transformer-remark</code>. As demoed below, add this plugin to the options of <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-transformer-remark</code>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-label=\"install permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save gatsby-remark-auto-headers</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-use\"><a href=\"#how-to-use\" aria-label=\"how to use permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to use</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// In your gatsby-config.js</span>\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-transformer-remark`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-remark-auto-headers`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Note: if you are using <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-remark-prismjs</code>, make sure that it’s listed after this plugin. Otherwise, you might face an issue described here: <a href=\"https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/issues/5764\">https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/issues/5764</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// good</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-transformer-remark`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n      <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-remark-auto-headers`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-remark-prismjs`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// bad</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-transformer-remark`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n      <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-remark-prismjs`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// should be placed after `gatsby-remark-autolink-headers`</span>\n      <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-remark-auto-headers`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"options\"><a href=\"#options\" aria-label=\"options permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Options</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><del><code class=\"language-text\">offsetY</code>: Signed integer. Vertical offset value in pixels</del> (this plugin is able to automatically connect headers and be able to calculate top correctly)</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">icon</code>: SVG shape inside a template literal or boolean <code class=\"language-text\">false</code>. Set your own svg or disable icon (optional)</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">className</code>: String. Set your own class for the anchor (optional)</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">maintainCase</code>: Boolean. Maintains the case for markdown header (optional)</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">attr</code>:String. Set the id to any property</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// In your gatsby-config.js</span>\nmodule<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-transformer-remark`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-remark-autolink-headers`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n              offsetY<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`100`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n              icon<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`&lt;svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\">&lt;path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\">&lt;/path>&lt;/svg>`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n              className<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`custom-class`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n              maintainCase<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n              id<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`data-id`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>","timeToRead":2}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-remark-auto-headers/","id":"40e267d1-d342-5f4b-bd66-80e1e15bc7fe","layout":"plugins"}}